text: @FedEx @FedExHelp on the phone w ur Bristol & being told that missing my required signature package 3x was my fault because FedEx only knock/ring bell as courtesy!! Well I call HORRIBLE SERVICE!! How can I sign if u don’t let me know u’re here!! When did this poor service start??

@sassy_art_is @FedEx Hello, my name is Karin. I apologize for the inconvenience this has caused and this is not the experience we want to provide. I would be happy to look into this matter, please DM the tracking number, delivery address and contact information. Thank you!
